        </item>
        <item>
            <title>馬斯克投資飛天車 Model A 試飛，無旋翼設計、售價 230 萬仍有逾 3 千人排隊</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/25/model-a-flying-car/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=model-a-flying-car</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/25/model-a-flying-car/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 05:24:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[飛天車]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293902</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日前網上流傳一段美國初創企業 Alef Aeronautics 試飛旗下飛天車 Model A 的影片，顯示飛行汽車技術邁向實用化新階段。據悉 Elon Musk 名下的 SpaceX 曾投資該公司。預計 Model A 最快可在 2025 年開始交付。Alef Aero 期望這項突破能為城市交通帶來翻天覆地的變革，為用戶提供靈活多變的通勤選擇。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293909" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/@NEWS9LIVE">NEWS9 Live@YouTube</a></p><p>外媒上傳的影片顯示，美國初創企業 Alef Aeronautics 成功試飛旗下飛天車 Model A，影片顯示，這款由 Tesla 行政總裁 Elon Musk 投資的創新飛行器 Model A 飛行器採用無旋翼垂直起降技術，據報 2025 年開始交付。據悉在充滿電的狀態下， Model A 可水平飛行 177 公里，在地面上續航力可達 322 公里。據《Channel C》報道指，美國聯邦航空管理局（FAA）已發出特別適航證書。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293907" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/@NEWS9LIVE">NEWS9 Live@YouTube</a></p><p>Alef Aero Model A 車體採用碳纖維物料製成，有效減輕重量並提升結構強度。Model A 可容納兩名乘客，具備垂直升降及水平飛行功能。車體旋轉時可由地面駕駛模式無縫切換至飛行模式，成功破解傳統飛天車機翼佔用空間的技術難題。Alef Aero 希望 Model A 能紓緩城市擠塞問題，特別適合短途通勤及地面駕駛結合的日常應用場景，為用戶出行提供「上天下地」的雙重選擇。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293908" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/@NEWS9LIVE">NEWS9 Live@YouTube</a></p><p>Model A 售價約 30 萬美元（約港幣 233.24 萬元），目前已有逾 3,000 人預訂，預計於 2025 年正式投產。Alef Aero 行政總裁 Jim Dukhovny 指，Model A 能在交通高峯時解決擁堵問題，更可在緊急情況下提供另類逃生途徑。他補充，公司正積極開發價格更親民的版本，希望普及飛天車技術，使更多人享受其帶來的便捷與創新。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_24890"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lCmfrCJBvSk?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>圖片、資料來源：<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/@NEWS9LIVE">NEWS9 Live@YouTube</a>、<a href="https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%9E%82%E7%9B%B4%E8%B5%B7%E9%99%8D-%E7%84%A1%E6%97%8B%E7%BF%BC-%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E5%8F%83%E6%8A%95-%E9%A3%9B%E5%A4%A9%E8%BB%8A-%E8%A9%A6%E9%A3%9B%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F-072002250.html">anue</a>、<a href="https://businessfocus.io/article/305207/%E9%A3%9B%E5%A4%A9%E8%BB%8A-alef-%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B">business focus</a>、<a href="https://channelchk.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%BB%8AModel-A%E8%A9%A6%E9%A3%9B%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F-%E5%94%AE%E5%83%B9%E9%80%BE30%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E5%B7%B2%E6%8E%A53%E5%8D%83%E5%A4%9A%E8%A8%82%E5%96%AE">Channel C</a>、<a href="https://www.startupselfie.net/2025/02/21/alef-aeronautics-drivable-flying-car-first-flight/">Startup selfie</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/25/model-a-flying-car/life-tech/auto/">馬斯克投資飛天車 Model A 試飛，無旋翼設計、售價 230 萬仍有逾 3 千人排隊</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
