            <title>配二代 UWB 晶片，定位範圍達 60 米，蘋果或於 5-6 月推 AirTag 2</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/25/apple-airtag2-findmy/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-airtag2-findmy</link>
